1. *Kuću* sam kupio pre nekoliko godina. (I bought *a house* a few years ago.)
2. U *kući* imamo pet soba. (We have five rooms in *the house*.)
3. Često *kuću* čistim vikendom. (I often clean *the house* on weekends.)
4. Za rođendan sam mu kupio novi *kućni* bioskop. (I bought him a new *home* cinema for his birthday.)
5. Svi smo u *kući* bili na okupu za Božić. (We all gathered together in *the house* for Christmas.)
6. *Kuća* je renovirana prošle godine. (The *house* was renovated last year.)
7. Nisam mogao da nađem ključeve za *kuću*. (I couldn't find the keys to the *house*.)
8. U parku je izgrađena nova *kućica* za decu. (A new *playhouse* for children was built in the park.)
9. Većinu vremena provodim u *kućnom* uredu. (I spend most of my time in my *home* office.)
10. Prošle nedelje sam posetio svoju baku u njenom *starom* selu. (Last week, I visited my grandmother in her *old* village.)